divs: Sighting Detailsi walked outside my west-facing door. i saw an airplane-typical-style-type-light; there is power lines to my west. while facing west, i observed this light go left and right, up and down in variations. it went up past one power line, then back down, then back up, etc., changed direction, and again was observed going up and down through the power lines then finally descended out of view west ward.
trends: There have been 5 other sightings in Norwalk
There were no other sightings in Norwalk on or around October 15th 2012
Summary: bright light going left, right, up, down,diagonal, eventually disappearing due to houses west of me
